<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Irregular" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Irregular,</orth> lawless, unprincipled: <cit><quote>leaving our rankness and i. course,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 5.4.54" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 4, 54</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>against the i. and wild Glendower,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.1.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 1, 40</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>wherein my youth hath faulty wandered and i.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 27</bibl></cit>.
